                              the main hand: መጋቢት: <locus target="#3r">fol. 3r</locus>. ሚያዝያ: <locus target="#9v">fol. 9v</locus>. ግንቦት: <locus target="#13r">fol.
                                 13r</locus>. ሰኔ: <locus target="#19v">fol. 19v</locus>. ሐምሌ: <locus target="#31r">fol. 31r</locus>. ነሐሴ: <locus target="#35v">fol.
                                 35v</locus>. መስከረም: <locus target="#42v">fol. 42v</locus>. ጥቅምት:
                                 <locus target="#48r">fol. 48r</locus>. ኅዳር: <locus target="#50v">fol. 50v</locus> ታሕሣሥ: <locus target="#54r">fol. 54r</locus>. ጥር:
                                 <locus target="#57v">fol. 57v</locus>. የካቲት: <locus target="#59v">fol. 59v</locus>. መጋቢት: <locus target="#76r">fol.
                              76r</locus>.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <desc>- Doodles: fols. 1r, 1v, 2r, 2v, 80r, 80v.</desc>
                        </item>
